us of our roots.

00:07:50.220 --> 00:07:52.263 position:50% align:center
[LEV]
What was it like?

00:07:52.347 --> 00:07:54.224 position:50% align:center
[IRINA]
Delicious.

00:07:54.307 --> 00:07:57.894 position:50% align:center
