00:08:06.945 --> 00:08:09.989 position:50% align:center
[LEV chuckles] If you guys
don't drink people's blood,

00:08:10.073 --> 00:08:12.909 position:50% align:center
then I don't get the whole
"cursed species" thing.

00:08:12.992 --> 00:08:15.120 position:50% align:center
It's all human nonsense.

00:08:15.203 --> 00:08:17.580 position:50% align:center
You see, back when
the plague occurred,

00:08:17.664 --> 00:08:20.667 position:50% align:center
your kind was looking for
someone to blame it on.

00:08:20.750 --> 00:08:22.794 position:50% align:center
Since then, that's the
way we've always been

00:08:22.877 --> 00:08:24.421 position:50% align:center
portrayed by your books.

00:08:24.504 --> 00:08:26.256 position:50% align:center
[LEV gasps]

00:08:26.339 --> 00:08:28.091 position:50% align:center
