which are made up of blood.

00:08:35.473 --> 00:08:36.641 position:50% align:center
What?

00:08:36.725 --> 00:08:39.019 position:50% align:center
In other words, it's a
substitute for blood.

00:08:39.102 --> 00:08:41.354 position:50% align:center
You have had milk before,
haven't you?

00:08:41.438 --> 00:08:42.939 position:50% align:center
Sure.

00:08:43.023 --> 00:08:45.400 position:50% align:center
Well...

00:08:45.483 --> 00:08:46.860 position:50% align:center
[LEV]
I don't get it.

00:08:50.363 --> 00:08:52.407 position:50% align:center
[LEV] In space, the ship's
temperature is controlled

00:08:52.490 --> 00:08:56.786 position:50% align:center
